<h1>107 instances of cross-agency searches</h1>

<p>Of the {{ dedupedStats.deduped | number }} deduplicated search sessions, <strong>{{ assistOther.total }} were conducted on behalf of or through coordination with other agencies</strong>: {{ assistOther.assistOtherCount }} explicitly cross-agency, {{ assistOther.statewideCount }} through statewide systems.</p>

<h2>Verify this yourself</h2>

<h3>Step 1: Download the data</h3>

<p><a href="{{ "/outputs/assist-other-agencies/assist-other-agencies.csv" | url }}" class="cta">Download assist-other-agencies.csv</a></p>

<p>Source file used for classification:</p>
<ul>
  <li><a href="{{ "/outputs/audit-logs-deduplicated/sopo-flock-audit-deduped.csv" | url }}">sopo-flock-audit-deduped.csv</a> (1,572 deduplicated search sessions)</li>
</ul>

<h3>Step 2: Open in a spreadsheet</h3>

<ol>
  <li>Open Google Sheets or Excel</li>
  <li>Go to <strong>File → Import → Upload</strong></li>
  <li>Upload <code>assist-other-agencies.csv</code></li>
  <li>Columns include all audit log fields plus <code>assist_label</code> and <code>assist_pattern</code></li>
</ol>

<h3>Step 3: Count by category</h3>

<ol>
  <li>In a blank cell: <code>=COUNTIF(K2:K, "assist-other")</code> to count explicit cross-agency searches</li>
  <li>Result should be <strong>{{ assistOther.assistOtherCount }}</strong></li>
  <li>In another cell: <code>=COUNTIF(K2:K, "statewide-system")</code> to count statewide-system searches</li>
  <li>Result should be <strong>{{ assistOther.statewideCount }}</strong></li>
  <li>Total: <code>=SUM(the two cells)</code> should be <strong>{{ assistOther.total }}</strong></li>
</ol>

<h3>Step 4: Spot-check the classifications</h3>

<ol>
  <li>Filter column K (<code>assist_label</code>) to <code>assist-other</code></li>
  <li>Look at column C (<code>Reason</code>) — you should see phrases like "Assist other", "assist other", "Assist other agency investigation"</li>
  <li>Now filter K to <code>statewide-system</code></li>
  <li>Look at column C — you should see "MIAC request", "MDEA Investigation", "mdea via miac"</li>
</ol>

<h3>Step 5: Verify from the source</h3>

<ol>
  <li>Open <code>sopo-flock-audit-deduped.csv</code> in a separate tab</li>
  <li>In column C (<code>Reason</code>), search for "assist" — count matches</li>
  <li>Search for "miac" or "mdea" — count matches</li>
  <li>These numbers should match the classified counts above</li>
</ol>

