<h2>Important caveats</h2>

<ul>
  <li>Not all MIAC/MDEA entries are cross-agency — some may be SPPD officers using statewide systems for their own cases.</li>
  <li>"File 1" is ambiguous — it may refer to another agency's file or SPPD's own.</li>
  <li>Reason text is self-reported by officers and has not been verified against case records.</li>
</ul>

